summary: This appears to be a brief email exchange from December 19, 2019, where an individual states they will be out of the country but in the same time zone and available to join a call on their cell phone. The document is part of the Epstein case files and shows communication regarding scheduling a call.

events.title: Scheduling of international call
events.description: An individual communicates that they will be out of the country but available to join a call on their cell phone as they are in the same time zone.

keyFacts: The document is an email dated December 19, 2019, regarding scheduling a call.
The sender indicates they will be out of the country but in the same time zone and available via cell phone.
The document is part of the Epstein case files (EFTA00079628, EFTA00079629).
